                <h1>How to Change Word Background Color: Black to White</h1>
                <p>To change the Word background color from black to white, open your document and navigate to the "Design" tab. Click on "Page Color" and select "White" from the options. You can also find this feature under "Format Background" if you're using an older version. Remember to save your changes for the new background color to take effect.</p>
